<text>Shallum (&quot;retribution&quot;) was the name of several people of the Old Testament.

==Shallum of Israel==
King of Israel.

==Alternative name of Jehoahaz==
King of Judah

==Son of Tikvah==
Keeper of the temple-wardrobe in the reign of Josiah (2 Kings 22:14) and husband of Huldah the prophetess.

